{"tid":887631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［我彈出又彈入］特朗普再稱中美貿易磋商有很大進展","createTime":"2018-11-03T05:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T09:15:37.000Z","uid":29540,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc133dba7cd0f78c6abaf12970a4699a505f386","tid":887631,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】美國總統特朗普再度提出，與中國的貿易磋商有很大進展。他的說法與白宮經濟顧問庫德洛的說法顯得不一致，庫德洛表示，並無所稱的可能達成貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易爭拗有望緩和，刺激美股道指初段揚198點，但庫德洛否認官員獲指示要起草對華貿易方案的報道，道指曾急挫301點，全日高、低位點數波幅擴至500點，其後特朗普再稱，與中國的貿易磋商有很大進展，與幕僚口徑不一致，道指借勢上行，收市只跌109點或0.43%；標指低收0.63%；納指則下滑1.04%。美國新增職位強勁，聯儲局12月再加息已無懸念，亦利淡美股。蘋果手機銷售遜預期，收市瀉6.6%，同樣拖累大市。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴第二財季盈利按年增6.17%，經調整每股盈利9.6元人民幣，高於預期的7.43元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=463358&amp;isapp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D463358%26isapp%3D1&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2812b59a\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=463358&amp;isapp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a461a8553ffa0abb96f8616f15dbeea3c3fc210","tid":887631,"uid":84771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"庫德洛未走淡倉"},{"pid":"bc3751a2784d281972954d64e4e94d0b533bdee0","tid":887631,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319f16fe271f18d291b0f61c22c76697eea4a4df","tid":887631,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"懷疑侵習扯貓尾炒牛熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e864b93bb50d8d162451fd0a1191e5581bd6968e","tid":887631,"uid":29540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/